Package sample

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Continent
    This class contains information about the continent and methods to store and retrieve information.
    Controller
    This controller class will controls the main user interface.
    GameDetails
    This class is used to store the initial game parameters.
    GameparametersDialogController
    This class contains the methods that are used to get the no of players based on the user selection and their characters and the choosen map.
    LoadgameController
    This class loads the map into game window panel.
    Main
    This class is the main class.
    Map
    This class is used to store the Map.
    MapEditorController
    This class displays the text area for the user to edit the map.
    NewMapController
    This NewMapController class is responsible for controlling the newmap window This class creates the Textarea to construct the newmap and saves the map if the map is valid.
    Player
    This class maintains the player details and implements methods related to the player.
    Territories
    This class is used to maintain territories and methods used to store and retrieve information.
